title: Jesse Livermore's Methods of Trading in Stocks (2012)
description:
Audio Books : Educational : Other quality : English

The material presented here first appeared as a continuing series of articles in the Magazine of Wall Street. They were obtained through exclusive interviews with Jesse Livermore by R.D. Wyckoff at a time when Livermore was the single most formidable factor in the market.

After being "lost" for many years, these interviews are now brought together in book format.

Enjoy and Seed!
